\u00f8tten.", "\u2013 Da baserer vi litt p\u00e5 CAS-behandlingen av saken mot Martin Johnsrud Sundby. Det var ikke det der dro av g\u00e5rde med de st\u00f8rste summene, sier Skogstad. Skiforbundet brukte totalt 3,3 millioner kroner p\u00e5 Sundby-saken."]}, {"field": "category0", "value": "100sport"}, {"field": "category1", "value": "100sport|vintersport"}, {"field": "category2", "value": "100sport|vintersport|langrenn"}, {"field": "contenthash", "value": "7c8306501c9e8334d2d54154dd9464cb2e7a5ca76a9fe4097e77ce5ef23a20a6"}, {"field": "createtime", "value": "2017-03-08T12:52:07.000Z"}, {"field": "description", "value": "Norges Skiforbund har s\u00e5 langt brukt mange hundre tusen kroner p\u00e5 advokathjelp til Therese Johaug. N\u00e5 risikerer langrennsstjernen \u00e5 miste all pengehjelp."}, {"field": "heading", "value": ["Skiledelsen i hastem\u00f8te for \u00e5 avgj\u00f8re Johaug-st\u00f8tte -adressa.no", "Anke fra FIS", "\u2013 En ny situasjon"]}, {"field": "id", "value": "8cc433e7725410269980b8416faba07e64724e29"}, {"field": "keyword", "value": ["Norge", "Norges Idrettsforbund", "Martin Johnsrud Sundby", "FIS", "Therese Johaug"]}, {"field": "keywords", "value": "Norge,Norges Idrettsforbund,Martin Johnsrud Sundby,FIS,Therese Johaug"}, {"field": "kw-category", "value": ["langrenn", "100sport", "vintersport"]}, {"field": "kw-classification", "value": "sports"}, {"field": "kw-concept", "value": ["st\u00f8tte", "skiforbund", "anke"]}, {"field": "kw-entity", "value": ["anke", "adresseavisen", "skiforbund", "norges idrettsforbund"]}, {"field": "kw-location", "value": "drammen"}, {"field": "kw-pageclass", "value": "article"}, {"field": "kw-person", "value": ["torbj\u00f8rn skogstad", "martin johnsrud sundby", "therese johaug"]}, {"field": "kw-taxonomy", "value": ["100sport/vintersport", "100sport/vintersport/langrenn", "100sport"]}, {"field": "og-image", "value": "https://vertical.snd.no/images/24831b9d-9621-4813-99f2-81823f6b8662?fit=crop&h=551&q=80&w=980"}, {"field"